# zgrab2 — application-layer banner-grab scanner (zmap). Built from pinned source.
# VERSION is our published image tag; REF is the exact upstream ref to build (tag,
# branch, or commit SHA). Bump REF to upgrade; the pipeline re-runs govulncheck +
# Trivy before publishing.
REPO=https://github.com/zmap/zgrab2
# Pinned to master e5172a7 (2026-06-12), NOT the v1.0.0 tag: v1.0.0 predates the
# `rdp` module (added upstream 2026-06-03) that the scanner-worker requires, and
# there is no upstream release containing rdp yet. Revisit when zmap tags a
# release that includes rdp.
VERSION=master-e5172a7
REF=e5172a71e6e725f5b2684b0006426ed6b540c63a
PKG=./cmd/zgrab2
BIN=zgrab2
GO_VERSION=1.25
# Security dep overrides — reachable govulncheck findings patched in our build
# (space-separated module@version). None needed at this ref: master already ships
# golang.org/x/net v0.55.0 (the GO-2026-5026 fix that v1.0.0 required a patch for).
GO_PATCHES=
